{"tid":1162011,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家有沒有想過楊過和小龍女如何過日子?","createTime":"2019-05-19T14:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T05:43:37.000Z","uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4aaa44c5e6d6b32f71a31701f3800ea195aac6eb","tid":1162011,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"在youtube網上相關推介<br />\n竟然有06年劉亦菲小龍女版本神鵰, 劉亦菲年青時的古裝真的如仙女般<br />\n當時直覺覺得楊過/戲中黃曉明就正啦, 溝到小龍女, 尹志明都不錯, 食左龍姑娘隻豬<br />\n<br />\n楊過和小龍女在神鵰終結時, 回到古墓生活<br />\n幸運的, 還有隻鵰比佢地撚, 沒有鵰, 實在想像不到他們如何生活?<br />\n古墓在現在西安市終南山隔離, 就是說他們回到古墓過野人般的生活<br />\n而且小龍女擺明係死魚, 古墓也沒有什麼好玩<br />\n下雨時, 應該周圍都是蚊<br />\n<br />\n其實大家有沒有想過楊過和小龍女如何過日子?"},{"pid":"80bfc8f7c43528748d93dd6be97cca707ca4acb7","tid":1162011,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"每日都在幹"},{"pid":"f0cb13855533e4021e697fbde140a083453cf271","tid":1162011,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"練功＋湊女"},{"pid":"89d3467af5c4cc18d1e6cada72562ece80d9cb7e","tid":1162011,"uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"日日練慾女心經"},{"pid":"44fa496daeacef4f0b65d6a3ecb9a96c090e8a67","tid":1162011,"uid":12558,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T22:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQKUPmx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQKUPmx.png&h=e10d1eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1uYVyOg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1uYVyOg.png&h=59a16a4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019版小龍女毛曉慧"},{"pid":"26081c3eb11a5b35015928b950355c1a671990aa","tid":1162011,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T23:17:31.000Z","msg":"一鳩日喺度姑姑... 姑姑... 姑姑... 姑到聽朝..."},{"pid":"cd27c0e3ca686ed2ccf769c808edc91774bfe988","tid":1162011,"uid":140798,"like":0,"di